<section class="about container">
  <h1>About This Training</h1>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>Backend Dev Training is a comprehensive, server-rendered training platform covering the essential skills every backend developer needs. Built with a backend-driven architecture using Node.js, Express, and EJS templates.</p>

    <h2>Architecture</h2>
    <p>This application follows a backend-driven architecture where all pages are rendered on the server. There is no client-side JavaScript framework — the server handles routing, data loading, and HTML generation. This approach offers fast initial page loads, better SEO, and simpler deployment.</p>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Runtime:</strong> Node.js</li>
      <li><strong>Framework:</strong> Express.js</li>
      <li><strong>Template Engine:</strong> EJS (Embedded JavaScript)</li>
      <li><strong>Architecture:</strong> Server-side rendering with MVC pattern</li>
      <li><strong>Styling:</strong> Vanilla CSS with Roboto Condensed</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Topics Covered</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>HTTP Fundamentals</li>
      <li>REST API Design</li>
      <li>Databases & Data Modeling</li>
      <li>Authentication & Authorization</li>
      <li>Middleware & Request Pipeline</li>
      <li>Error Handling & Logging</li>
      <li>Testing Backend Code</li>
      <li>Security Best Practices</li>
      <li>Performance & Caching</li>
      <li>Deployment & DevOps</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

